 (x+y)^n = \sum\limits_{k = 0}^n x^ky^{n-k} 
 (p+1-p)^n = \sum\limits_{k = 0}^n p^k(1-p)^{n-k} = 1 
 \sum\limits_{k = 1}^n p^k(1-p)^{n-k} = 1 - p^0(1-p)^{n-0} = 1 - (1-p)^n \\ 1-(1-p)^n = 1 - \left(\frac{49}{50}\right)^n \ge \frac{1}{2} \\ \frac{1}{2} \ge \left(\frac{49}{50}\right)^n \\ \ln{\frac{1}{2}} \ge n \ln \frac{49}{50} \\ \frac{\ln{1} - \ln{2}}{\ln{49} - \ln{50}} \le n \\ n \ge \frac{\ln{2}}{\ln{50} - \ln{49}} 
P_{all}=(\frac{49}{50})^N
1-P_{all} \ge 50\%
0.5 \ge (\frac{49}{50})^N
 N \ge \lceil\frac{ln(0.5)}{ln(49/50)}\rceil = 35
